 415:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *
 416:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   This function initializes the component’s global variables and initiates
 417:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   communication with the host by pull-up D+ line.
 418:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *
 419:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** * \param device:
 420:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   Contains the device number of the desired device descriptor. The device
 421:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   number can be found in the Device Descriptor Tab of "Configure" dialog,
 422:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   under the settings of desired Device Descriptor, in the *Device Number*
 423:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   field.
 424:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *  \param mode:
 425:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   The operating voltage. This determines whether the voltage regulator
 426:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   is enabled for 5V operation or if pass through mode is used for 3.3V
 427:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   operation. Symbolic names and their associated values are given in the
 428:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *   following list.
 429:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *
 430:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *       *USBFS_DEBUG_3V_OPERATION* - Disable voltage regulator and pass-
 431:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *                                      through Vcc for pull-up
 432:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *
 433:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *       *USBFS_DEBUG_5V_OPERATION* - Enable voltage regulator and use
 434:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *                                      regulator for pull-up
 435:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *
 436:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *       *USBFS_DEBUG_DWR_POWER_OPERATION* - Enable or disable the voltage
ARM GAS  C:\Users\yoons\AppData\Local\Temp\ccJHkSRb.s 			page 14


 437:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *                                      regulator depending on the power supply
 438:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *                                      voltage configuration in the DWR tab.
 439:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *                                      For PSoC 3/5LP devices, the VDDD supply
 440:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *                                      voltage is considered and for PSoC 4A-L,
 441:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *                                      the VBUS supply voltage is considered.
