 832:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *
 833:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *  This function returns the activity status of the bus. It clears the hardware
 834:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *  status to provide updated status on the next call of this function. It
