 883:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *  when the host sends double SET_CONFIGURATION request with the same 
 884:Generated_Source\PSoC5/USBFS_DEBUG.c **** *  configuration number or changes alternate settings of the interface. 
